# Optional override for the site origin used in canonical URLs, Open Graph /
# Twitter tags, JSON-LD @ids, the sitemap and robots.
#
# The app already defaults to https://arlindminushi.com (see lib/site.ts), so you
# do NOT need to set this in production. Set it only to override — for example to
# test production metadata locally:
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000
